## 六、变更前必须检查

修改任何模块前，先检查影响范围：

```bash
# 修改 Agent 运行时前
rg "from owlclaw.agent" owlclaw/ --glob "*.py"

# 修改治理层前
rg "CapabilityVisibilityFilter\|governance" owlclaw/ --glob "*.py"

# 修改 Hatchet 集成前
rg "hatchet\|integrations.hatchet" owlclaw/ --glob "*.py"
```

